nhc_headline: ...HURRICANE WATCH ISSUED FOR PORTIONS OF SOUTHERN MEXICO...
summary: ...HURRICANE WATCH ISSUED FOR PORTIONS OF SOUTHERN MEXICO... As of 9:00 PM CST Mon Jun 16 the center of Five-E was located near 11.2, -92.6 with movement WNW at 12 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
